         <div xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874"><!-- p1l1-r7 -->
           <head xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Hd1e108">Rubrica 7</head>
           <head xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De misericordia et clementia</head>
           <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-d1e114">
           ¶ De misericordia et cle<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>mentia dei. Rubrica. 7.
        </p>
           <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-d1e121">
           <lb ed="#O"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Rd1e118">Psalmista psalmus 32</ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Qd1e120">misericor<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>dia 
           domini plena est terra.</quote> 
        </p>
           <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-d1e130">
           <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Rd1e130">Idem 136 psalmus.</ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Qd1e132">oculi domini super timentes 
           <lb ed="#O"/>eum: et in eis qui sperant super 
           <lb ed="#O"/>misericordia ei. </quote> 
        </p>
           <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-d1e141">
           ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Rd1e145">83 psalmus.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Qd1e143">misicordi<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>am 
           et ueritatem diligit deus. </quote>
        </p>
           <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-d1e149">
           ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Rd1e155">84 psalmus.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Qd1e151">
           <lb ed="#O"/>misericordia et veritas obuiauerunt 
           <lb ed="#O"/>sibi: iustitia et pax osculate sunt. </quote>
        </p>
           <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-d1e159">
           <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Rd1e169">102 psalmus.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Qd1e161"> misericordia domini ab eterno et vsque 
           <lb ed="#O"/>in eternum super timentes eum. </quote>
        </p>
           <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-d1e167">
           ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Rd1e183">117 
           <lb ed="#O"/>psalmus.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Qd1e171">Confitemini domino quoniam bonus 
           <lb ed="#O"/>quoniam in eternum mia eius. </quote>
        </p> 
           <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-d1e177">
           ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Rd1e195">167 psalmus.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Qd1e179"> 
           <lb ed="#O"/>Beneplacitum est domino super timentes 
           <lb ed="#O"/>eum: et in eis qui sperant super misericordia 
           <lb ed="#O"/>eius. </quote> <!--line bumps down-->
        </p> 
           <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-d1e187">
           <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Rd1e209">Pa <!--line bumps up--> ralipomenon li. i. capitulo 21.</ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Qd1e191">Cum <!--line bumps back down--> venisset gad angelus ad 
           <lb ed="#O"/>dauid. dixit ei. <unclear> hec </unclear> dicit dominus: 
           <lb ed="#O"/>Elige quod volueris: aut tribus annis
           <lb ed="#O"/>pestilentiam: aut tribus mensibus 
           <pb ed="#O" n="11-v"/>
           <cb ed="#O" n="a"/> 
           <lb ed="#O"/>fugere hostes tuos: et gladium eorum 
           <lb ed="#O"/>non posse aut tribus diebus gla<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>dium 
           domini interficere in uniuersis 
           <lb ed="#O"/>sinibus isrili. Nuc igitur vide quid 
           <lb ed="#O"/>respondeam ei qui me misit. </quote>
           <!--left off here-->
        </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-d1e213"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Qd1e215" source="http://scta.info/resource/Ichr21_13@1-29 http://scta.info/resource/Ichr21_14@1-6"> Et dixit <name ref="#David">dauid</name> ad
        <name>gad</name>: Ex omni parte me angustie premunt. Sed
        melius mihi est vt incidam in manns domini: quia
        multe: sunt miserationes eius: quam in manus
        hominum. Misit egrso dominus pestilentiam in israel </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-d1e227">
               
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Rd1e253">hieremias propheta in li. lamenta. c. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Qd1e231" source="http://scta.info/resource/lam3_32@3-10">Si
        abiecerit dominus et miserebitur secundum multitudinem <!--the word dominus is not included in the biblical text and some spelling differences-->
        miserationum suarum.</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-d1e239">
               
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Rd1e267">Iesus filius sirach in ecclesiastico. c. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Qd1e243" source="http://scta.info/resource/sir5_5@8-12 http://scta.info/resource/sir5_6@1-11">Non
        adijcias peccatum super peccatum: et ne dicas mi
        seratio dei magna est: multitudini peccatorum <!-- neque vs non in the bible vs the text-->
        meorum miserebitur</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-d1e253"> /
       <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Rd1e281">17.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Qd1e255">Om magna mina domini
        et propitiatio illius conuertentibus ad se. </quote>  <!--can not find a corresponding verse-->
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-d1e261"> /
       <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Rd1e291">18.
        c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Qd1e263" source="http://scta.info/resource/sir18_4@8-12">Quis adijciet enarrare misericordiam dei. </quote> <!--eius vs dei used-->
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-d1e269">
               
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Rd1e304">Pilon vel philemon li. sapientie. c. 15.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Qd1e273" source="http://scta.info/resource/sap15_1@1-13">Tu
        deus noster suauis et verus es: patiens cum
        minsericordia disponens omnia. </quote> <!--some textful differences in terms of words included or not-->
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-d1e282">
               
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Rd1e319">Mattheus in euang. c. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de1874-Qd1e286" source="http://scta.info/resource/mt5_7@1-6">Beati misericor <!--28.xml-->
        <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
                  des: quoniam ipsi miseri cordiam consequentur. </quote> <!--some textful differences but quite similar-->
            </p> 
         </div>
